4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp aimed at individuals looking to become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. It covers essential areas including Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish, accommodating diverse learners. For more details, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop